VERSION
  Show server version and game configuration.

SYNTAX
  version
  vers

DESCRIPTION
  Displays the Empire server version string and key configuration
  values for this game instance:
    - World size (width x height in sectors)
    - ETU per update (Economic Time Units — the update granularity)
    - Update interval (real-world seconds between updates)
    - Tech and research multipliers
    - Which optional game features are enabled

  Use this to understand the rules and scale of the current game.

EXAMPLE
  version                   see server version and config

SEE ALSO
  update  show  info
